---
title: Chickpea-Powered Mediterranean Couscous with Roasted Veggies and Feta
description: You haven’t tasted chickpeas until you’ve tried them roasted. Trust us, the delicious crunch is absolutely worth the time spent in a hot oven. They’re tossed with bubbly Israeli couscous,  roasted veggies, and smoked paprika for a mishmash of savory Mediterranean flavors.
